Class PoliticalParty

java.lang.Object
PoliticalParty
public class PoliticalParty extends Object
Contains information regarding a political party for ClosedpartyList election. Stores the name of the party and a queue of the names of candidates within that party. Also includes the number of votes received, number of seats, and the remainder of votes to be used for calculating seat allocation.
